Sistema de Banco da Tivic: (SBT[rsrs]) 

Modulos do sistema:

--- User
 -> id:String
 -> name:String
 -> password:String
 -> idAccount:String
 -> createdAt:Timestamp with time zone
 -> updatedAt:Timestamp with time zone 
 
--- Account
 -> id:String
 -> balance:Number
 -> createdAt:Timestamp with time zone
 -> updatedAt:Timestamp with time zone 

Services:
--- User
 -> Create
 -> List
 
--- Account
 -> CRUD
 -> verifyBalance():Number
 -> deposit():void
 -> withdraw():void
 
Banco de dados: 

 -> sqlite
 
Front-end:

 -> Angular 8+
